1
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:06,640
No.

2
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,920
I can't wait any longer.

3
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,000
I'm going to find Huanghuacai.

4
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,130
Brother, calm down.

5
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:12,360
I've already sent someone to look for her.

6
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:13,160
Young Master.

7
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,530
Miss Shen is badly hurt.

8
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:21,840
Shen Qiangwei, how did you end up like this?

9
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:23,120
Who did this?

10
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:25,520
Ah Fu, who did this?

11
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,320
Ah Fu.

12
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,620
Where did you find her?

13
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:30,280
The Young Madam told me to watch the Prime Minister's Manor.

14
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,160
Then I saw Second Miss Shen's guard,

15
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,090
throw out a sack.

16
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,039
When I went closer to check,

17
00:01:34,039 --> 00:01:35,320
it turned out to be Eldest Miss Shen.

18
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,720
Go get a doctor, quickly.

19
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,680
Is the Third Prince here?

20
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:44,840
Brother Bai.

21
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,680
Third Prince.

22
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,080
Who hurt you like this?

23
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,759
It was Shen Lingbo.

24
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,640
Shen Lingbo?

25
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:58,080
How... how dare she do this to you?

26
00:01:58,479 --> 00:02:00,520
Aren't you the Emperor's concubine?

27
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:03,480
Shen Lingbo is a lunatic.

28
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,360
She wants to usurp the throne.

29
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,080
What did you say?

30
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:12,120
She conspired with Tuoya to frame Marquis Bai,

31
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,400
framed him for Bulei's death,

32
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:21,980
and spread rumors that the Song Army was colluding with the enemy.

33
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:24,079
She doesn't just want revenge.

34
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:29,680
She wants to drive you all to your deaths, step by step.

35
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,600
She even wants...

36
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,760
She even wants to get rid of you.

37
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,720
But why would she do that?

38
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,720
For Bai Manchuan.

39
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:45,320
This way, she can have Bai Manchuan all to herself.

40
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,520
She wants to trample everyone under her feet.

41
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,040
She is just a lunatic.

42
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,720
Miss Shen, stop talking.

43
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:54,680
I...

44
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,400
I'll take you to the Imperial Physician.

45
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,720
It's too late.

46
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,840
She wanted me to take medicine to fake a pregnancy.

47
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,880
I refused.

48
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,560
She told me to frame you.

49
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,760
I refused that too.

50
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:10,240
She... she wanted to silence me.

51
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,360
Miss Shen, don't speak.

52
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,880
Third Prince.

53
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:19,520
Don't call me Miss Shen anymore.

54
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,520
Call me Qiangwei.

55
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:25,920
Okay?

56
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:26,520
Qiangwei.

57
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,720
Hold on.

58
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,720
Qiangwei!

59
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:36,440
She... she's dead.

60
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,400
Brother.

61
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,760
Miss.

62
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,400
Miss, you're awake.

63
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,520
Why did you come out?

64
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,780
You scared me to death.

65
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,640
Didn't I die?

66
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,600
You might not believe it,

67
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,840
but the squad we've been searching so hard for

68
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,680
has actually been by your side all along.

69
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,680
For all these years,

70
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,399
they have been secretly protecting you.

71
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,519
The reason you survived the ambush this time

72
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,980
is because they saved you.

73
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,480
They saved me?

74
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,760
This is the token they left behind.

75
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:32,080
It has the character 'Xuan' carved by the Master himself.

76
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,740
The Master had long predicted

77
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:36,159
that the Emperor would be wary of the Song Army.

78
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:38,960
Master said if the political situation ever changed,

79
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,840
and the court could no longer tolerate the Song Family Army,

80
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,159
you must not be without a trump card in your hand, Miss.

81
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:46,159
So, under the guise of reorganizing border defenses,

82
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:49,890
he secretly gathered elites from all over to form this squad

83
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,600
to guard you at all times.

84
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,400
Father.

85
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,800
What about the Marquis's Manor?

86
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,520
What is the situation there now?

87
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,560
Marquis Bai...

88
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,360
Marquis Bai has already been thrown into the Imperial Prison.

89
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,080
Someone accused him of colluding with the enemy and treason,

90
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,560
and murdering Prince Bulei.

91
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,760
I went to check today,

92
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:20,000
and found the entire Bai Manor under surveillance.

93
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,920
No one can enter or leave freely.

94
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:27,480
Now, Young Master Bai and Miss Bai are both under house arrest.

95
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,040
It's Shen Lingbo.

96
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,960
They've made their move.

97
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:35,520
Linlang, assemble the Song Family Army squad immediately.

98
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:38,680
Miss, won't that expose us?

99
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,240
Marquis Bai is in prison,

100
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,250
the Bai family is confined,

101
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,400
and the Third Prince is isolated and helpless.

102
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,040
We have no other choice.

103
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,000
The Song Family Army squad

104
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,400
is the only card Father left me.

105
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:01,960
It is time for us to fight back.

106
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:07,260
Notify the squad to assemble in the south of the city immediately.

107
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:07,880
Yes.

108
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,400
Please protect me.

109
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,960
Manchuan, you're finally here.

110
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,800
What exactly do you want?

111
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,320
Why do you all love asking that question?

112
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,120
I don't want to play games with you.

113
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:35,920
You framed the Bai family and the Song Family Army,

114
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:38,780
and used Bulei to gain the Third Prince's trust.

115
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,560
What is your goal?

116
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,040
All I've ever wanted

117
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,720
from beginning to end,

118
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,360
is you.

119
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,920
You did all this

120
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,680
just for me?

121
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:57,640
Manchuan, I've never begged you for anything.

122
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,800
But now, I only ask you to really look at me.

123
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,680
Lingbo.

124
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:06,000
You didn't do any of this for me.

125
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,960
You did it for yourself.

126
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,560
You want power and dignity.

127
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:13,240
You want to stand high above and look down on everyone.

128
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,080
You're just using love as a guise

129
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:17,580
to pave the way for your own ambition.

130
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,920
I love you so much.

131
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,160
How can you say that about me?

132
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:24,120
Look at me. Tell me.

133
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:27,960
Have you ever, even for a moment, had feelings for me?

134
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,320
Never.

135
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,960
Couldn't you lie to me just once?

136
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,120
Say you care about me.

137
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,760
Say I matter to you.

138
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,680
Lingbo.

139
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,080
Turn back.

140
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,320
As long as you're willing to stop,

141
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,120
I'll find a way to save you again.

142
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,040
Just like that.

143
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:46,880
Manchuan.

144
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,159
You know exactly what kind of person I am,

145
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:51,159
yet you're still willing to save me.

146
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,960
But I can't turn back.

147
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,400
Tell me.

148
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:58,940
Where is Song Xuan?

149
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,160
Song Xuan?

150
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,280
Song Xuan isn't here.

151
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,760
I can give you a clue about her.

152
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,890
Speak. What are your terms?

153
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,120
You have to trade yourself for it.

154
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,240
What do you mean?

155
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:18,120
If you want to know where Song Xuan is,

156
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,480
stay with me tonight,

157
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,600
and I'll tell you.

158
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,930
You're humiliating me.

159
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,000
No.

160
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:26,360
I just want to know if in your heart,

161
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,680
she is worth stripping for.

162
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:51,760
Are you really willing to trample on your dignity for her?

163
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,680
She is.

164
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,680
Tell me.

165
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,760
Where is Song Xuan?

166
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,360
Get out! Get out of here!

167
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,240
Manchuan.

168
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:09,320
Do you regret saving me?

169
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,360
If you could do it all over again,

170
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,850
would you still save me?

171
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,360
Manchuan.

172
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,360
I truly love you.

173
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:50,480
Miss Shen, I've handled the people for you.

174
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:54,570
Zhongyi Marquis Manor is focused on the Third Prince right now.

175
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,080
Plus, Bai Manchuan and Song Xuan aren't there.

176
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,920
Now is the time to kill.

177
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,780
Find where Bai Chuyi is hiding immediately,

178
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:05,400
and kill her.

179
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:06,760
Yes.

180
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:35,960
How does that feel?

181
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,520
How did you...

182
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:46,320
You were too overconfident.

183
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,160
What should we do?

184
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,760
Young Master! Young Master!

185
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,720
Outside...

186
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:57,850
Princess Tuoya and Miss Shen have surrounded the manor.

187
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,400
The Marquis isn't the only one in this manor.

188
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,660
We're here too, right?

189
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,480
Right! We're here!

190
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,080
Don't be afraid, Young Master.

191
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,240
This knife has chopped plenty of ribs.

192
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,360
I'll chop up a few thieves before I die!

193
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,440
Right, everyone?

194
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,760
Yes! Let's fight!

195
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:11,840
What about you guys?

196
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,770
We spent years on the battlefield.

197
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,820
These soldiers are nothing to us.

198
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,960
Go, go!

199
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:19,320
Go!

200
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,760
Just go!

201
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:25,320
I'm counting on you all.

202
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,160
Young Master!

203
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,160
Go!

204
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,360
Go, Young Master!

205
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,160
Leave it to us.

206
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,680
Block the door!

207
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:40,920
Charge!

208
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:43,840
Hold the line!

209
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,290
The Bai Manor

210
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,240
will fight to the death!

211
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:03,800
Search the place!

212
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:08,520
Princess,

213
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,780
there's no one inside.

214
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,400
They can't have gone far.

215
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,400
After them!
